00:18:19.779 --> 00:18:24.549
It’s a hugely interesting topic, and although English may be a useful

00:18:24.549 --> 00:18:29.079
language, and there are many excellent reasons to learn it, it is

00:18:29.129 --> 00:18:33.799
just one of nearly 7,000 languages that are spoken around the world.

00:18:34.639 --> 00:18:40.719
A world where we all just speak one of a handful languages is a less rich, less

00:18:40.719 --> 00:18:46.719
diverse one, but unless there is a conscious effort to protect and encourage the

00:18:46.719 --> 00:18:51.649
